==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Uralite
<hw>U"ral*ite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[So called because
first observed in the <ets>Ural</ets> Mountains.]</ety>
<fld>(Min.)</fld> <def>Amphibole resulting from the alternation of
pyroxene by paramorphism. It is not uncommon in massive eruptive
rocks.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Uralitization</ent>⟦br⟧
